title: ArmA 2 - 2081 Missions Pack
description:
A mission renaming (classing to be specific ie. game type and max player number) project.

Originally started to make mission selection when administering servers faster, easier and specific to player numbers and desired mode (extremely helpful).

With the rather large number of missions renamed I thought it might be of some worth to the community/fans.


These missions require only Official Content:  A2  OA  BAF  PMC  ACR.


Pack contains 2081 mission
